---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — PawHaus"
  description="PawHaus privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal data in compliance with Singapore's PDPA."
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Privacy Policy' }]} />

  <section class="container-max pb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-light mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed text-sm">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          PawHaus ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with
          Singapore's Personal Data Protection Act 2012 (PDPA). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
          use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you visit our website or make a purchase.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">We may collect the following personal data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>Name and contact information (email address, phone number)</li>
          <li>Shipping and billing address</li>
          <li>Payment information (processed securely by Stripe — we do not store card details)</li>
          <li>Order history and shopping preferences</li>
          <li>Communications you send to us (emails, contact form submissions)</li>
          <li>Website usage data (cookies, analytics)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">We use your personal data to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>Process and fulfil your orders</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your orders and enquiries</li>
          <li>Send marketing communications (only with your consent)</li>
          <li>Improve our website and product offerings</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">We work with trusted third-party service providers to operate our business:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li><strong>Snipcart</strong> — Shopping cart and checkout processing</li>
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — Secure payment processing</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — Website hosting and security</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">These providers process your data in accordance with their own privacy policies and applicable data protection laws.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was
          collected, including for legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. Order data is retained for
          a minimum of 5 years for tax and legal compliance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">6. Your Rights Under PDPA</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">Under Singapore's PDPA, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate personal data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</li>
          <li>Request information about how your data has been used or disclosed in the past year</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">7. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses cookies to provide essential shopping functionality (e.g., shopping cart)
          and to analyse website traffic. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">8. Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data
          against unauthorised access, loss, or misuse. All payment transactions are encrypted using SSL
          technology and processed by Stripe.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your data protection rights,
          please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@pawhaus.com" class="text-coral hover:underline">hello@pawhaus.com</a><br />
          <strong>Address:</strong> PawHaus, Singapore
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
